## 1. Baseline requirements
- All production artifacts (containers/packages) must be **signed**.
- Verification enforced at deploy time ("deny unsigned" policy).

## 2. Key management
- Key storage: HSM/KMS.
- Rotation: at least yearly (baseline), every 6 months (regulated) or upon incident.

## 3. Pass/fail criteria
- [ ] 100% of production artifacts signed.
- [ ] Verification enforced in production.

## 4. Evidence
- Policy configs, verification logs, rotation history.
